wight Yorke|Yorke]] {{goal|76||80}}\n|goals2     = \n|location   = [[Trafford]], [[Greater Manchester]]\n|stadium    = [[Old Trafford]]\n|attendance =55,187 \n|referee    = \n|result     = L\n|id=}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round      = 4\n|date       = 21 August 1999\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Leeds United A.F.C.|Leeds United]]\n|score      = 2\u20131\n|report     = [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/sport/football/fa_carling_premiership/426643.stm Report]\n|team2      = [[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]]\n|goals1     = [[Lee Bowyer|Bowyer]] {{goal|51}}<br>[[Danny Mills|Mills]] {{goal|72}}\n|goals2     = [[Kevin Phillips (footballer)|Phillips]] {{goal|37|pen.}}\n|location   = [[Leeds]], [[West Yorkshire]]\n|stadium    = [[Elland Road]]\n|attendance =39,064 \n|referee    = \n|result     = W\n|id=}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round      = 5\n|date       = 23 August 1999\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Leeds United A.F.C.|Leeds United]]\n|score      = 1\u20132\n|report     = [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/sport/football/fa_carling_premiership/428385.stm Report]\n|team2      = [[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]]\n|goals1     = [[Rigobert Song|Song]] {{goal|20|o.g.}}\n|goals2     = [[Titi Camara|Camara]] {{goal|45}}<br>[[Lucas Radebe|Radebe]] {{goal|55|o.g.}}\n|location   = [[Leeds]], [[West Yorkshire]]\n|stadium    = [[Elland Road]]\n|attendance =39,703 \n|referee    = \n|result     = L\n|id=}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round      = 6\n|date       = 28 August 1999\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|Tottenham Hotspur]]\n|score      = 1\u20132\n|report     = [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/sport/football/fa_carling_premiership/432524.stm Report]\n|team2      = [[Leeds United A.F.C.|Leeds United]]\n|goals1     = [[Tim Sherwood|Sherwood]] {{goal|36}}\n|goals2     = [[Alan Smith (footballer born 1980)|Smith]] {{goal|53}}<br>[[Ian Harte|Harte]] {{goal|83}}\n|location   = [[London Borough of Haringey|Haringey]], [[London]]\n|stadium    = [[White Hart Lane]]\n