gn=\"left\"|22||align=\"left\"|DF||align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Michael Duberry]]\n|12+1||1||1||0||0+1||0||1||0||14+2||1||4||1\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|23||align=\"left\"|MF||align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[David Batty]]\n|16||0||0||0||2||0||4||0||22||0||4||0\n|}\n\n==Transfers==\n\n===In===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Date\n! Pos.\n! Name\n! From\n! Fee\n|-\n|15 June 1999\n|DF\n|[[Danny Mills]]\n|[[Charlton Athletic F.C.|Charlton Athletic]]\n|\u00a34,000,000\n|-\n|9 July 1999\n|DF\n|[[Michael Duberry]]\n|[[Chelsea F.C.|Chelsea]]\n|\u00a34,500,000\n|-\n|23 July 1999\n|FW\n|[[Michael Bridges]]\n|[[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]]\n|\u00a35,000,000\n|-\n|11 August 1999\n|FW\n|[[Darren Huckerby]]\n|[[Coventry City F.C.|Coventry City]]\n|\u00a34,000,000\n|-\n|19 August 1999\n|DF\n|[[Danny Hay]]\n|[[Perth Glory FC|Perth Glory]]\n|\u00a3200,000\n|-\n|17 December 1999\n|MF\n|[[Jason Wilcox]]\n|[[Blackburn Rovers F.C.|Blackburn Rovers]]\n|\u00a33,000,000\n|-\n|15 January 2000\n|GK\n|[[Danny Milosevic]]\n|[[Perth Glory FC|Perth Glory]]\n|\u00a3110,000\n|-\n|5 March 2000\n|GK\n|Shaun Allaway\n|[[Reading F.C.|Reading]]\n|\u00a3300,000\n|-\n|15 May 2000\n|MF\n|[[Olivier Dacourt]]\n|[[RC Lens]]\n|\u00a37,200,000\n|}\n\n===Out===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Date\n! Pos.\n! Name\n! To\n! Fee\n|-\n|11 June 1999\n|DF\n|[[Gunnar Halle]]\n|[[Bradford City A.F.C.|Bradford City]]\n|\u00a3200,000\n|-\n|15 June 1999\n|MF\n|[[Lee Sharpe]]\n|[[Bradford City A.F.C.|Bradford City]]\n|\u00a3200,000\n|-\n|30 June 1999\n|MF\n|[[David Wetherall]]\n|[[Bradford City A.F.C.|Bradford City]]\n|\u00a31,400,000\n|-\n|16 July 1999\n|FW\n|[[Clyde Wijnhard]]\n|[[Huddersfield Town A.F.C.|Huddersfield Town]]\n|\u00a3750,000\n|-\n|4 August 1999\n|FW\n|[[Jimmy Floyd Hasselbaink]]\n|[[Atl\u00e9tico Madrid]]\n|\u00a312,000,000\n|-\n|6 August 1999\n|FW\n|[[Derek Lilley]]\n|[[Oxford United F.C.|Oxford United]]\n|\u00a375,000\n|-\n|1 October 1999\n|FW\n|[[Paul Shepherd]]\n|[[Ayr United F.C.|Ayr United]]\n|Fr